item.title: My Taste
item.description: What is a “favorite” to me? Anime We are going to keep it to one instance of a story, regardless of medium. Otherwise, I would probably have multiple instances of Steins; Gate, Berserk, and Hunter x Hunter on my list. I’ll talk about this in my Honorable Mentions.
